attr.title: Brave Dogs Road
attr.desc: Brave Dog's Road is a short platformer about a dog who dreams of adventure. The game was created by Shawn as a learning tool to explore all aspects of game development. It features charming pixel art and multiple endings based on collecting claws.
attr.inst: Download game from https://puppiesandanime.itch.io/brave-dogs-road , place data.win in /ports/bravedogsroad/gamedata.
